Overview
--------
Provides core functionality for various projects implemented by Blackened Systems.

This project is open source, see the file: 'LICENSE' for terms and conditions.

Language: Scala
Build Tool: maven

MongoDB
-------
As of early 2011, Blackened Systems decided to use MongoDB as their primary datastore.  Consequently, the
code within this project has been written against that database.  Casbah was chosen as the library to facilitate
communication between the Scala layer and MongoDB.

